ELIGIBILITY REQUIREMENTS:

Proof of Canadian Citizenship;
The Co-op student must be able to obtain reliability status security clearance and maintain it for the duration of the co-op term;
If the student has listed a permanent address in a foreign country in the last five years, the student will need to obtain a document from that foreign police department stating that no infractions were committed throughout the duration of their stay.

Essential Qualifications:

1st or 2nd year Mechanical, Software or Electrical Engineering Student;
Initiative;
Dependability;
Knowledge of the MS Office Suit, MATLAB and VISIO;
Ability to organize and manage multiple projects;
Ability to carry out projects independently;
Effective communication skills;
Technical report writing;

Asset Qualifications:

DND/Navy familiarity;
Supervisory experience;
Project management experience;

